Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:04.87,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know that I've ever\N{\fs30}我不知道我曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:09.60,subTitle,,0,0,0,,been able to do anything.\N{\fs30}可以做什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.42,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I say it as a sort of,\N{\fs30}我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.04,subTitle,,0,0,0,,because I'm aware that it can be a strength\N{\fs30}是因为我知道这可能是一种优点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.46,subTitle,,0,0,0,,but it can also be a weakness\N{\fs30}也可能是一种缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.57,subTitle,,0,0,0,,because the focus is obsessive\N{\fs30}因为成为众人的焦点令人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.80,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and so when I go for something,\N{\fs30}所以当我要做某事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.07,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I go for it at the expense of everything else.\N{\fs30}我会对每件事都倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:28.03,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And I love what I do, simply,\N{\fs30}说白了 就是热爱我所从事的职业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.96,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and I feel so lucky that\N{\fs30}我感到非常幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.20,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to do it\N{\fs30}我能成为演员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:34.04,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and that I get to do it for a living\N{\fs30}同时还能以演戏为生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.87,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and cinema and theater have had\N{\fs30}电影院、剧院对我一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.63,subTitle,,0,0,0,,such a profound effect on me in my life.\N{\fs30}都产生了深远的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:42.20,subTitle,,0,0,0,,It's just a gut feeling.\N{\fs30}这是一种直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:45.76,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I think I always trust my gut,\N{\fs30}我一直相信我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:46.86,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that's all I have,\N{\fs30}一向如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.90,subTitle,,0,0,0,,even when I'm working.\N{\fs30}甚至是在我工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.61,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And you're thinking about the shape of a scene\N{\fs30}当你在想场景的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:52.77,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and how it should be played\N{\fs30}还有场景该如何进行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.90,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and your head can often get in the way\N{\fs30}你的大脑总会干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:55.90,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and you've got to trust your gut.\N{\fs30}你得相信你的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:01:01.91,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And it's just if I'm inspired,\N{\fs30}如果我受到启发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.08,subTitle,,0,0,0,,if my curiosity is peaked,\N{\fs30}如果我非常好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:07.69,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and I want to chase this possibility down,\N{\fs30}我想追寻这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.96,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that I see in front of me on my desk,\N{\fs30}我知道坐在桌子前的f
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.08,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and some of you may have heard me say this before.\N{\fs30}有些人可能之前已经听我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:17.64,subTitle,,0,0,0,,And I'm embarrassed to say,\N{\fs30}我很不好意思地说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.14,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I always speak in metaphors,\N{\fs30}我总是通过比喻来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.64,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to speak in any other way\N{\fs30}因为我不知道用其他方式如何表达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.64,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and for me, acting is kind of like playing the piano\N{\fs30}对我来说 表演有点像弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.04,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and if the piano is the human condition\N{\fs30}如果把钢琴比作人体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:34.16,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and we all have every single note\N{\fs30}我们都有每一个音符
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.96,subTitle,,0,0,0,,on that 88 key board within us\N{\fs30}存在于我们体内的88个琴键
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:42.38,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and for me, every role, \N{\fs30}对我来说 每个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.44,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to play every note\N{\fs30}我都希望能演好它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:48.80,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and sometimes if a character or a story\N{\fs30}如果一个角色或故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.28,subTitle,,0,0,0,,seem to stretch me in some way,\N{\fs30}在某种程度上吸引我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:56.01,subTitle,,0,0,0,,seems to offer up an experience that is new,\N{\fs30}给我一种全新的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.35,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that is a different chord or a different tune,\N{\fs30}一种不同的和弦或曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.88,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that is real and true,\N{\fs30}那种情深意切的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.90,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and human and accessible,\N{\fs30}深入人心的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:08.07,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and no matter how joyous or loving or warm,\N{\fs30}无论多么欢乐、热爱或温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.18,subTitle,,0,0,0,,or how dark or painful,\N{\fs30}亦或多么黑暗、痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.60,subTitle,,0,0,0,,if it seems like an interesting shape to inhabit,\N{\fs30}如果它是一个有趣的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.98,subTitle,,0,0,0,,I know if I'm running towards it already.\N{\fs30}我知道我已经为它准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.21,subTitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, couple of basic things,\N{\fs30}好的 一些基本的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.60,subTitle,,0,0,0,,be on time,\N{\fs30}守时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.34,subTitle,,0,0,0,,never underestimate the\N{\fs30}千万不要低估
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.87,subTitle,,0,0,0,,importance of punctuality,\N{\fs30}守时的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.05,subTitle,,0,0,0,,be prepared,\N{\fs30}做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.35,subTitle,,0,0,0,,you can never be over-prepared\N{\fs30}准备得再充分都不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:30.51,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and be true to yourself\N{\fs30}做真实的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.61,subTitle,,0,0,0,,and if you have something\N{\fs30}如果你有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.16,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that you want to say\N{\fs30}迫不及待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.89,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that you've been burning to say,\N{\fs30}想说的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.89,subTitle,,0,0,0,,don't ever let anyone tell you\N{\fs30}永远不要让任何人告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.40,subTitle,,0,0,0,,that you can't say it.\N{\fs30}你不能说
